    "body": "~A simple way to do this would be to introduce a `BlobCollation` class similar to the `Collation` class, but using the field type `binary` for `transactions` and `witness_nodes`. `Collation` could inherit from `BlockCollation` (sharing the header access helpers like `shard_id` etc.).~\r\n\r\nNot necessary as the original `Collation` class is not needed anymore. We can just rename and adapt it accordingly. Only problem is that existing tests will break, but until phase 2 they can be retired anyway.",
